    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the meat-free mince is browning, top, tail, peel and grate your <strong>carrot[s]</strong></p><p>Combine your <strong>sriracha</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and <strong>rice vinegar</strong> in a bowl with a pinch of<strong> sugar</strong> and 1 tbsp<span class=\"text-purple\"><span class=\"text-danger\"> [1 1/2 tbsp] </span>[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>water</strong></p><p>Add the<strong> grated carrot</strong>, then give it a good mix up and set aside – this is your <strong>spicy carrot quick-pickle</strong></p>",
