    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the meat-free mince has browned, add your <strong>ginger & garlic paste</strong> and cook for 1 min</p><p>Add your <strong>red chilli relish</strong>,<strong> tamari soy sauce</strong> and <strong>remaining toasted sesame oil</strong> and give it a good mix up – this is your <strong>meat-free mince bulgogi</strong></p>",
